  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You begin to nurture your abilities with the Sōzō clan's dojutsu, the Naibugan, an eye of immaculate vitality and cellular analysis. At 1st level, you gain access to <em><strong>Sōichi</strong></em>. You gain access to more Naibugan advancements as you reach higher levels. You can activate the Naibugan as a bonus action and it remains active for up to 10 minutes. For the duration, you can deactivate and reactivate the Naibugan at no additional cost. You can use the Naibugan twice before needing to take a long rest to regain its uses. Once its uses are expended, you can activate the Naibugan again by spending 10 chakra.</p>",
